  "body": "This is an antipattern, and makes it very hard to install in an existing virtual environment (for example, it clashes with web3==5.16.0)\r\nThe pip package requirements should contain loosened requirements for dependency packages.\r\nFor example, instead of eth-account==0.5.2, have eth-account>=0.5.2,<0.6, for example",
